{
  "id": 9,
  "title": "#9 Leaving Methana to Poros",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Sad news..."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "It was time to leave Methana."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Happy news."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "To celebrate our parting from the island. Alex made us a delicious Greek style pie. Adam says it was in the top five things he's ever eaten. It was pretty damn good ."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/98f29438-21b5-4380-8f96-54e224103fab/IMG_6998.jpeg",
      "caption": "Vegi pie"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/992338f0-a161-4103-a02e-ee373a667e0e/IMG_7041.jpeg",
      "caption": "leaving Methana"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "I really enjoyed Methana. It's definitely a very special place, with a lot of unique history. I'm very happy we spent five days here. We met some amazing people. People are really kind :)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Yesterday we got lots of recommendations from Elias. he told us all the amazing spots to visit in the Peloponnese."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/e1480138-ebba-4db6-a18e-95b80cb568d2/IMG_7002.jpeg",
      "caption": "Leaving Alex and Lotus land"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "So we left around 6 PM to the first 30 km away called Poros."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/f426bba8-9123-48db-bb97-17bc1c5f536d/IMG_7020.jpeg",
      "caption": "Poros view from the mainland"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Poros it's a beautiful small island, with little shops, and many many boats docked or acred."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/106f42ee-39ea-44fe-b6ce-568c57946310/IMG_7022.jpeg",
      "caption": "Small 1 euro ferry to Poros"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Elias told us about a quiet beach in the corner of the island to camp on."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/30e57ca2-33ca-4cde-a086-f827080e4895/IMG_7037.jpeg",
      "caption": "Beach camp on Poros"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Today we are off to the next stop :)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "-Erik"
    }
  ]
}